    {
      "text": "Dahna: Megami Tanjō (Dahna 女神誕生; Dahna: Goddess' Birth) is a 1991 platform action game developed by and published by IGS for the Mega Drive exclusively in Japan and South Korea. The player controls the woman warrior-like title character who struggles against the powers of an evil sorceress raiding her village. The story is told through cutscenes as Dahna is helped along the way by various mythical beasts.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Dahna: Megami Tanjō (ダーナ 女神誕生) est un jeu vidéo de type Beat them all sorti en 1991 sur Mega Drive. Le jeu a été développé puis édité par IGS.",
